Hey, am using a graphql request to grab to values from the CRM objects, but wanted to be able to set a default value for the name attribute for objects in the query that does not have a value for that property. I have looked through some HubSpot documentation for a couple hours now but can't seem to find anything. How can I in the graphql file set a default value for the name attribute for objects that are missing a value there. Here is my current graphql code: query CompanyQuery {
  CRM {
    company_collection {
      items {
        name
      }
    }
  }
}
